I can sit for hours and hours listening to the playlists on physicalfilms, a YouTube channel. The channel hosts numerous jazzy, house, garage, funk, Ibiza style music hits. If you are interested, make sure you visit the channel. Here are links to some of my favorite playlists:

item.title: Nicolas Jaar
item.dc:creator: anautonomousagent
item.description: American-Chilean DJ Nicolas Jaar knows how to produce those creative tunes that you immediately love. A friend described Jaar’s music as sexy Latin house and minimal music; I became hooked. His style is unique and chill. Here is an interview of Jaar. I suggest you explore Jaar’s music on SoundCloud or YouTube playlist or some of these: Nicolas Jaar – […]
item.content:encoded:
American-Chilean DJ Nicolas Jaar knows how to produce those creative tunes that you immediately love. A friend described Jaar’s music as sexy Latin house and minimal music; I became hooked. His style is unique and chill. Here is an interview of Jaar. I suggest you explore Jaar’s music on SoundCloud or YouTube playlist or some of these:

Nicolas Jaar – Episode 52 (feat. The Essential Mix 2012) Part 1

Nicolas Jaar – (Keith Jarrett – Tokyo, November 14)

Mi Mujer – Nicolas Jaar

El Bandido – Nicolas Jaar

Space Is Only Noise (Full Album) – Nicolas Jaar

Nicolas Jaar – Slices (DVD Feature)
